Dengue mortality

indi_0014_res <- indi_0014(
  agg = "mun_res",
  agg_time = "month",
  ano = 2000:2023,
  pop_source = "datasus2024",
  adjust_rates = FALSE
)
indi_0014_res |>
  filter(cod == 330455) |>
  mutate(
    date = as.Date(paste0(substr(date, 0, 4), "-", substr(date, 6, 7), "-01"))
  ) |>
  ggplot(aes(x = date, y = value)) +
  geom_line() +
  labs(
    title = "Dengue mortality",
    subtitle = "Rio de Janeiro, RJ",
    caption = "per 100,000 inhab."
  )
